00:10:19.860 --> 00:10:24.860
Jehovah will miraculously save his people throughout the great tribulation

00:10:24.860 --> 00:10:27.860
and arrange for their survival.

00:10:27.860 --> 00:10:32.860
Today, the faithful slave was put in charge of providing spiritual food

00:10:32.860 --> 00:10:36.860
for God's people who number into the millions.

00:10:36.860 --> 00:10:41.860
The slave also shows complete trust in Jehovah that he will guide them

00:10:41.860 --> 00:10:44.860
with his Holy Spirit.

