Jesus, in turn, provides direction for his people through the faithful

00:11:09.860 --> 00:11:12.860
and discreet slave.

00:11:12.860 --> 00:11:17.860
We can have, therefore, full confidence in the scriptural insight,

00:11:17.860 --> 00:11:22.200
understanding and guidance.

